title: Rescue crews searching LA River after car found in water near South Gate
text:
tweet KABC 
Rescue crews are searching the Los Angeles River after a car was found in the water in South Gate near the 710 Freeway. KABC Saturday, February 11, 2017 10:23PM Rescue crews are searching the Los Angeles River after a car was found in the water near the 710 Freeway in South Gate.Authorities are not sure how long the vehicle has been in the water or if anyone was injured, but nobody was found inside the vehicle.DEVELOPING: We will provide details as they become available.
